{"tid":1191414,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"對人幾好都唔會有回報 咁點解一開始唔做個仆街","createTime":"2019-06-08T01:58:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T03:22:27.000Z","uid":207383,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d7be6c5afd837ef53ba213d72afee0e06bb912bb","tid":1191414,"uid":207383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T01:58:03.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以駁吓我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb88e5feca0e65ac783445da96a12f34634c6c53","tid":1191414,"uid":229589,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d7be6c5afd837ef53ba213d72afee0e06bb912bb","tid":1191414,"uid":207383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T01:58:03.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以駁吓我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T02:06:00.000Z","msg":"唔會駁你，我認同你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6117061535958350fd50164b295388331f03ba9","tid":1191414,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T02:09:02.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"1cf68ecaa1e2099eb7955a130e442347f988d483","tid":1191414,"uid":249647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d7be6c5afd837ef53ba213d72afee0e06bb912bb","tid":1191414,"uid":207383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T01:58:03.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以駁吓我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T02:18:01.000Z","msg":"你會唔會諗下辜負你嗰個人其實都曾經好似你咁諗，俾人傷害左後就做左仆街傷害其他人<br />\n一愛傷害就立即向極端方向思考係失敗既行為<br />\n不如思考下如何俾到保護自己時，亦可以正面咁去面對人<br />\n我相信善意係呢個世界上最重要既野<br />\n人生課題呀CHING"},{"pid":"c2d134f972337e061d0af1820290eae66c7a17a0","tid":1191414,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T02:20:24.000Z","msg":"曾經，我試著逃避。<br />\n曾經，我害怕得到。<br />\n曾經，我嘗試放棄。<br />\n曾經，我的世界只有黑。<br />\n而你，讓我從黑色中找到這片白。<br />\n後來，我拼命的抓住那片白。<br />\n後來，我放棄了自己的黑給你所有的白。<br />\n後來，我生命中只剩下了白。<br />\n後來，我以為我的世界都是白。<br />\n後來，我失去了自己失去了那片白。<br />\n後來，我把你推到了我曾經的黑。<br />\n後來，我們都迷失在一片黑。<br />\n後來，最終發現我的黑你永遠也不懂。<br />\n最後，我的黑不是黑是沒有了白的黑。<br />\n因為你，我懂了灰永遠失去了白。"},{"pid":"291e45d7b615a4c5fe1fa08fc8b6d3a952d5df5b","tid":1191414,"uid":187098,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T02:31:14.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講下你對人有幾好<br />\n然後你又想要咩回報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a710cc5fe3dfc4897ee01c1cccf4aa75d1a94c22","tid":1191414,"uid":207383,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cf68ecaa1e2099eb7955a130e442347f988d483","tid":1191414,"uid":249647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d7be6c5afd837ef53ba213d72afee0e06bb912bb","tid":1191414,"uid":207383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T01:58:03.000Z","msg":"有冇人可以駁吓我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T02:18:01.000Z","msg":"你會唔會諗下辜負你嗰個人其實都曾經好似你咁諗，俾人傷害左後就做左仆街傷害其他人<br />\n一愛傷害就立即向極端方向思考係失敗既行為<br />\n不如思考下如何俾到保護自己時，亦可以正面咁去面對人<br />\n我相信善意係呢個世界上最重要既野<br />\n人生課題呀CHING"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T02:32:49.000Z","msg":"已經俾人辜負n次 我先會有呢個諗法<br />\n一直做好人已經做到攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c733a3ddb2dd75eb15fae8b9228eb3cf84e9c38a","tid":1191414,"uid":249647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a710cc5fe3dfc4897ee01c1cccf4aa75d1a94c22","tid":1191414,"uid":207383,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cf68ecaa1e2099eb7955a130e442347f988d483","tid":1191414,"uid":249647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d7be6c5afd837ef53ba213d72afee0e06bb912bb","tid":1191414,"uid":207383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T01:58:03