"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T03:17:39.000Z","msg":"做仆街通常最後都無咩朋友 頂得順咪繼續<br />\n做好人，對人好，就算10個入面有1個會欣賞你<br />\n你慢慢累積到就係一班有心人 <br />\n<br />\n自己參透下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你要駁我一定駁到<br />\n自己諗下點做人"},{"pid":"629ea3e1b364d2dc75b2c5b7f97688152fbee9ed","tid":1191414,"uid":238415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T03:22:27.000Z","msg":"點對人係要睇回報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"}]}